Title: Act Your Age
Plot: A 6-year-old girl suffers ailments expected in patients much older. Tensions between Chase and Cameron lead House to intentionally assign them to the same tasks, including investigating the young girl's home.
GuestStars: Marcus Folman, Ellery Sprayberry, Joel David Moore, Carla Gallo, Slade Pearce, Bailee Madison, Erich Anderson
